  <brief_title>THE FACTORS AFFECTING THE ADHERENCE TO THE PULMONARY REHABILITATION PROGRAM IN COPD</brief_title>
  <official_title>INVESTIGATION THE FACTORS AFFECTING THE ADHERENCE TO THE OUTPATIENT PULMONARY REHABILITATION PROGRAM IN COPD</official_title>
